## Development Commands

**Package Manager:** Always use `pnpm` (not npm or yarn)

```bash
# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Start development server with Turbopack
pnpm run dev

# Build for production
pnpm run build

# Start production server
pnpm start

# Lint code
pnpm run lint
```
